- Clean up the isPREEnabled/isLoadPREEnabled/isLoadInLoopPREEnabled/isLoadPRESplitBackedgeEnabled block to restore valid definitions.
- Replace the malformed performPRE signature with a safe stub that returns false to avoid PRE.
Then I will rebuild with submit-patch and run the reproducer.

```bash
